properties.description: beginning where the county lines of San Luis Obispo, Kings and Kern Counties converge, the county line also being the township line between T.24S. and T.25S., in R.16E.
westerly direction along this county line for 42 miles to the range line between R.9E. and R.10E.
southerly direction for 12 miles along the range line to the southwest of corner of T.26S. and R.10E.
